{"tid":1719567,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【歷史重溫】請回憶721後香港人係點樣擊退黑社會","createTime":"2019-11-14T06:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T09:10:39.000Z","uid":131691,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ce6bdddcb64de78355720e30facca9792c47fa55","tid":1719567,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:24:29.000Z","msg":"黑社會簡介：<br />\n人：廢老（體質差），休班警（體質好）<br />\n攻擊：遠攻比警甴低（冇子彈，冇催淚，冇水炮，只有零星炮仗），近攻比警甴高（刀，鎚仔）<br />\n防禦：零<br />\n數量：視乎人工<br />\n士氣：視乎人工及攻勢<br />\n紀律：零<br />\n<br />\n香港人721後對策：<br />\n先被撳住嚟打（未研發對策）<br />\n再煲大內外輿論嘅嘩然（依然輸緊）<br />\n再文宣connect警黑合作（政治上拉政權落水）<br />\n再拎gear反攻（開始贏）<br />\n效果：勇武成為市民嘅救星<br />\n<br />\n論反攻gear：<br />\n黑社會用嘅都係高殺傷力但低range嘅武器，如刀，鎚仔，伸縮警棍等<br />\n而且毫無紀律，淨係識扮型，冇人數優勢都狗衝<br />\n所以香港人一係用人海圍毆<br />\n一係用竹，矛，長遮（記得係插，唔係扑）等武器反攻<br />\n<br />\n上幾次北角嘅福建幫就係被竹同木棍打返轉頭敗走。"},{"pid":"951727be4fb0a764a744495e02b918de6611d9c0","tid":1719567,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:26:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2462e26eb0aa9c67c79984522c20f29fd2130e2d","tid":1719567,"uid":61282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:26:24.000Z","msg":"長遮用嚟捅人、插人、用遮頭遮尾挑，唔好劈打"},{"pid":"97d3e3153c4f5cf20a8bbb39b5e7810da95404bc","tid":1719567,"uid":45741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0682da30265bcf3928dd62b64f5c2cc357ed55","tid":1719567,"uid":109115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:27:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebbf11555f2351283f54dc9f877b7ccf52043a57","tid":1719567,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T06:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac00790ee998f3a1303